flowchart LR
    L0[L0 Direct<br/>local / reversible / low risk] --> L1[L1 Micro-plan<br/>few clear steps]
    L1 --> L2[L2 Plan iterations<br/>multi-step implementation]
    L2 --> L3[L3 Independent checks<br/>audit / review / research]
    L3 --> L4[L4 Route exploration<br/>architecture choice]
    L4 --> L5[L5 Deep branching<br/>prototype / high uncertainty]

    R1[Scope] -.increases.-> L5
    R2[Risk] -.increases.-> L5
    R3[Planning] -.increases.-> L5
    R4[Need for audit/report] -.increases.-> L5
    R5[Need for approval gates] -.increases.-> L5
